---------------------------------------------------

			!!! WARNING !!!
Opening a file OVERWRITES it!

How to save *this* file:
1) Move the file to your 
   desired location.
2) Rename the file if needed.
3) Open the file.

Tips:
- If you quit without opening
  a file, the save operation
  is cancelled.

